cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CR 

This paper is primarily focused on scene understanding and segmentation tasks, which are typically associated with the computer vision (cs.CV) and robotics (cs.RO) sub-categories. The use of deep learning and normalizing flow also suggests a strong connection to machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper addresses the issue of out of distribution data, which is a common concern in computer security (cs.CR).
